  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ecef60b6-ef05-4323-9c22-16f32895ce9d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ecef60b6-ef05-4323-9c22-16f32895ce9d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/984b52ef5c68c557.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/984b52ef5c68c557.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/984b52ef5c68c557.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18baefb4-3247-4ecf-a4dc-1df1eb678b94\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7f8440a7-960a-4f79-8323-736bb5a06055\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ac6312cc-76ba-45d1-9319-f3fff5b08e08\">안녕하세요. </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3e48d3dc-966a-432e-8be8-525bdcac2ff7\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c306f47-658e-4fec-8e6c-5aa6449cdc53\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5c640d4e-aff0-4f4f-bb9c-9263e71e0972\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bcb2f6f8-d9ad-40d1-aea4-0ba1cb28afb2\">오늘은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c60f32b-9b04-4891-a8cd-2bf30b0ddcd4\"><b>건강과 장수, 두 마리 토끼를 모두 잡을 수 있는 건강 실천방식</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-934ed20a-93d3-4ee5-a6b8-78673d1a1afc\">에 대해서 말씀드리고자 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0b2e0e4-8517-40cc-a582-5dd8c01d2cac\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f0b2e0e4-8517-40cc-a582-5dd8c01d2cac\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aab7996470ae2cde.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aab7996470ae2cde.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/aab7996470ae2cde.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-411999d2-b8da-48d9-bfcc-c853746d9cdb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-01f50327-6344-4ab6-b302-7f60980cf093\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0aeb1202-0e76-4c20-89ed-ad411af01304\">대부분의 사람들이 건강한 몸으로 오래 살고 싶은 마음이 있을 거라고 생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6a690242-675f-4588-90ee-b29549b10cf1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-349d7984-ec71-4e25-80b8-32847351b962\">그러나 도대체 어떻게 하면 건강하게 장수할 수 있을까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c7964f66-9744-49b5-9bfd-3c263ec084df\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c7964f66-9744-49b5-9bfd-3c263ec084df\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79981b7a0f0f4ea6.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79981b7a0f0f4ea6.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/79981b7a0f0f4ea6.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7427862a-cce0-408b-af07-2256010431a8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-984210d2-ef2b-42ac-9834-d5dfadf5b555\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5c04b994-e162-4a77-8a08-7dc4531f5e77\">건강과 장수의 실천방식은 바로 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7fe210a7-1bb4-43e3-8775-536d9c300e04\"><b>칠금문</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cea25bcc-bbb9-4215-a103-f91c7c176a35\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-053ba597-531a-4152-bc89-b8d974b5ee54\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-559193c8-8906-46c5-8724-18247d3f283a\"><b>칠금문</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0014424e-884b-4aea-833d-b293ecf33104\">이란, 과거 선사 </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c74b15df-c10c-4e0a-93b6-8832a234f7f7\"><b>태을진인</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-da2cc35c-3312-494d-a6f9-53c155461e57\"><b>(太乙眞人)</b></span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cc54569e-929b-4a88-8b54-c8004f6f1d3f\"><b>의 양생 비결</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-353eb98e-ec83-4c3b-b313-4f7240d1b426\">인데요, 지금부터 하나씩 설명해 드리도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2b0fdff-593f-4950-8715-e19044881863\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d2b0fdff-593f-4950-8715-e19044881863\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a31b567ca9c35099.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a31b567ca9c35099.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a31b567ca9c35099.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b176af3e-450a-419e-b240-52815d83a325\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87b224cf-34fb-4857-bc13-a0b196ef0f2b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8d2145a9-3ef1-491d-ac5d-e001859a6b3b\">칠금문의 첫 번째는 바로 </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-130ad45c-3bbe-4b09-be24-3910ada1cc47\">말을 적게 하여 &#x27;내기&#x27;를 기르는 것</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6d4fc778-03e3-4c4d-8dc4-1249a140ca75\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20827515-0f8e-467b-b61c-7b9f8b4befa1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5d71eb04-7b32-4688-ba60-b1fa619c712e\">말하는 것은 생각보다 더 많은 기운을 소진시키는 행위로 남을 헐뜯는 말이나 필요하지 않은 말은 하지 않는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b99f3e67-a7bb-4e61-bceb-93471f0e5cae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-10d65cea-c18b-4e41-95ff-bdaea884726a\">필요한 말만 한다면 내적 기운을 빼앗길 일이 없기에 말은 신중하고, 적게 하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9eb38516-bde0-4b45-a42b-566f586eeea9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9eb38516-bde0-4b45-a42b-566f586eeea9\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7ba4921e3b64ad81.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7ba4921e3b64ad81.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7ba4921e3b64ad81.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-afc4fed4-f0ab-42df-8c3d-4219edaccf76\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4b3d36f7-409c-47da-977f-9ec5df2b2670\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8f03e033-f22f-4270-b60f-71af51aa52ef\">두 번째로는, </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-be93dc0f-5cf9-4355-b8f2-90cb08a4543a\">색욕을 조심해 &#x27;정기&#x27;를 기르는 것</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-da46ed87-12b8-48e9-ac0f-3a983abab0cc\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0f838123-234f-408b-8e21-bcc432aea5c9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-53556fb4-dbbb-4ce2-b25d-3c66cdc4b85e\">문란한 성생활은 정을 낭비하게 하여 질병에 걸리기 쉽기 때문에 내 곁의 반려와 몸과 마음으로 애정을 나누는 것이 장수에 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4046b20a-1609-4b40-814c-ff70f3e5daff\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4046b20a-1609-4b40-814c-ff70f3e5daff\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fdef4f001bc7345f.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fdef4f001bc7345f.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fdef4f001bc7345f.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42292eb6-af73-463b-8461-0eede8d05cbf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e385aadb-65fb-4b8d-a677-ac79739884b3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-47ff9f71-3a68-4e17-9586-7d1afe47d5e5\">세 번째는, </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d5bf5fc-5d4d-4e79-a27d-40cf781ec644\">입맛을 담백하게 하여 &#x27;혈기&#x27;를 기르는 것</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6743beb5-8f9b-4259-a38f-4f244b8e69a1\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9312ebc2-2afd-44d3-a93e-cc7b27d6c130\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6d8e2594-897b-4306-9e1a-20aca80588fe\">육류처럼 기름진 음식보다 채소처럼 담백한 음식을 섭취하면 피를 맑게 하는 데 큰 효과가 있고 이는 당뇨, 비만, 고혈압 등을 예방하는데 효과가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fad16777-f815-4692-91bd-b30c35ff2fdf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fad16777-f815-4692-91bd-b30c35ff2fdf\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d921665b56dedd4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d921665b56dedd4.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6d921665b56dedd4.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2de8aa69-67db-4f36-8ae9-c12ca68ff76d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d6bedfad-d3ef-4b4f-a03a-bc00dd5f1292\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8c2c72d1-ebe8-4fe3-8c6d-4b20a1c7a78b\">네 번째는 </span><span style=\"background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9045a6d5-7ca4-484d-91f6-192cd966c51f\">&#x27;오장의 기운&#x27;을 기르는 것</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7ff49718-d408-45ca-a0ea-69c888275361\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2573bb8-a7a2-499a-809e-5b85a61fc7e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-00b978e2-5fcf-4e83-b085-94041ce6d5bf\">침은 신장의 진액으로 이를 귀중히 여겨야 장수할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be44a8d4-f418-4dce-8968-c0df2d0e3167\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-88c0b5e2-50d8-4a4f-9d7b-83627bced605\">&lt;동의보감&gt;에도 무병장수하는 방법 중 하나로 침을 자꾸 만들어 삼키는 방법이 제시되어 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b82b7c9b-a675-4dd1-a4d7-b244da10e4f3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n 