></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-82ba4408-9b57-4464-b49d-3eaab043aa27\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2056ab3a-d062-41b1-941b-9e63cee7a1aa\">화를 내는 것은 간의 건강에 치명적이며 스트레스를 많이 받게 되면 간에 무리가 가 얼굴빛이 어두워지게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5de058d2-b806-4eb8-af62-067f486ab308\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-802f9491-e7ec-49ac-a5d2-958f8c9fa6d7\">때문에 마음을 가꾸는 것이 장수의 기본이라고 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-26f70fde-f87e-4051-b7fd-dbeee7c1211c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-26f70fde-f87e-4051-b7fd-dbeee7c1211c\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bd17c03b7e838205.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1920\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bd17c03b7e838205.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bd17c03b7e838205.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"888\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </di